     л  
     л  Co-written by Zak Penn, the screenwriter of movies X2: X-Men 
     л  United and X-Men: The Last Stand, and legendary comic book writer
     л  Chris Claremont, X-Men: The Official Movie Game immerses players 
     л  in an original storyline that provides the back-story for the 
     л  upcoming X-Men: The Last Stand feature film. For the first time
     л  ever, the game enables players to truly command the powers of 
     л  popular characters from the X-Men movie universe by allowing 
     л  players to assume the roles of Wolverine, Nightcrawler, and 
     л  Iceman as they wield and upgrade their signature powers and 
     л  maneuver through unique environments designed to showcase their
     л  Super Hero abilities. Assisted by other X-Men characters, players
     л  will use an advanced control scheme to master and control the 
     л  characters like never before as they unleash Wolverines combat 
     л  rage, experience Nightcrawlers acrobatics and teleportation 
     л  powers, and glide through the air on Icemans ice slide.
